'''Quests''' are groups of interrelated tasks, usually involving a story line, that can take anywhere from a few minutes to a few hours or even a few days to complete.

The starting locations for all quests are labelled with a blue compass [[icon]] {{SCP|Quest}} on the [[minimap]], and completing them can provide rewards ranging from experience and items, to access to new areas, [[minigames]] and [[miniquests]].

As of {{Globals|latest quest release date}}, there are a total of {{Globals|quests}} quests in ''[[Old School RuneScape]]'' with {{Globals|quests f2p}} [[free-to-play|free]] and {{Globals|quests p2p}} [[member]]-only quests. The first quest was [[Cook's Assistant]] and the most recently added quest is {{Globals|latest quest p2p}}. A total of {{Globals|quest points}} [[Quest points]] are rewarded for the completion of all quests, including {{Globals|quest points f2p}} quest points from quests available to free players. Players who have obtained the maximum number of quest points are entitled to purchase and wear the [[quest point cape]].

